     C/EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      * *INZSR - Program Initialisation routine                       *
      *****************************************************************
     C     *INZSR        BEGSR
 
     C     *ENTRY        PLIST
 
      ** Inputs
      ** Return Code
     C                   PARM                    RetCodeIn
 
      ** Other parms
 
      ** Automatic Closure Indicator
     C                   PARM                    DDACIN
 
      ** Outputs
 
      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      ** Automatic Closure - OK
     C                   PARM                    DDACINOK
 
